== English ==
===Etymology===
Via Yiddish < Hebrew verb [[ידע]] (''yadáa'', to [[know]]).

===Alternative spellings===
* yadda yadda yadda
* yadda, yadda, yadda

===Phrase===
'''yada yada yada'''  (or ''yada, yada, yada'')

# and so on, and so forth.

===Usage notes===
Normally used mid-sentence.

